==Hunting technique==
The hunting technique is the same as for other [[salamander]]s. Players must bring a [[rope]] and [[small fishing net]] for each [[net trap]] they plan to set up. Clicking on a [[young tree]] will set the trap. Players can use the same rope and net over and over to catch multiple creatures.

===Multiple traps===
Net trapping can be done with multiple traps at once, with the maximum amount of traps depending on the player's Hunter level.

Compared to hunting other salamanders, an extra trap may be set while hunting black salamanders, since they are located in the [[Wilderness]].

